{"tid":1382667,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"與其call消防，不如人人係消防","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T18:20:53.000Z","uid":167595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c93fb04b19a74d768a61373451407918405c16c","tid":1382667,"uid":167595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:57:21.000Z","msg":"見到好多post話成立民間自衛隊或保安公司，如果經警務處發牌相信冇乜可能會批，成本亦應該會好高，冇牌就會面對裝備唔合法問題<br />\n<br />\n有人話call消防救人，消防始終係編制下紀律部隊，上頭既order都要服從，未必次次都出到黎救人<br />\n<br />\n有冇考慮過眾籌收購或成立一間消防公司同業餘消防隊，俾有心為香港出一分力既人加入<br />\n亦都可以合法持有較專業既gear，係唔同場合應付有可能發生既火警<br />\n<br />\n大家集思廣益，有冇法律同消防人士講下意見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36b89345421f56b4ec207d01a2fe888fc4d9b3c","tid":1382667,"uid":41705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382502/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382502/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d2c8be85b25e693f474a2f951e591cdf0e7f4bc5","tid":1382667,"uid":167595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望有人俾下意見"},{"pid":"fc47b514e23348848503c1816f4eb91d6d51014c","tid":1382667,"uid":293816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5eb2a2d1563099fd8d92134de6bcb3109c3a1a69","tid":1382667,"uid":241750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:20:53.000Z","msg":"冇呢方面嘅專業知識<br />\n只可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}